1. Sibling project: afm (Apache-2.0 OR MIT)
================================================================================

afm-epub depends on the `afm` library crates (`afm-syntax`,
`afm-encoding`, `afm-parser`) consumed via git tag dep, to convert
Aozora Flavored Markdown sources into the XHTML fragments that EPUB3
spine items embed. afm itself is dual-licensed under Apache-2.0 OR MIT
and ships its own NOTICE file naming the upstream comrak fork and the
CommonMark / GFM / Aozora Bunko material it incorporates. Refer to
https://github.com/P4suta/afm/blob/main/NOTICE for the authoritative
chain.


